Data structure is a physical organization of memory that stores that stores data in two patterns.
1.Linear Data structure
2.  Non Linear Data structure

1. Linear Data Structure - 

A linear data structure are the design in linear fashion where the data accessed in linear order that is one by one.
The linear data structure is classified in following
1. Array
2. Linklist
3. Stack
4. Queue

2. Non-Linear Data Structure-

In this structure that grows in any direction according to the need. In non- linear fashion where the data can be accesed in any order.
The non  linear data structure are classified into following
1. Tree
2. Graph
3. Hash
